  <discussion>The record of Telesonix jamesii from New Mexico is based on poor material and should
        be regarded as provisional. There is a report (J. G. Packer and D. H. Vitt 1974) of this
        species (or T. heucheriformis) from Laramie Mountain, Wyoming; no voucher specimens have
        been seen.</discussion>
